<lb n="0928b11" ed="T"/>馱<g ref="#CB00576">𩕳</g><note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引一</note>麼抳麼抳<note place="inline">一</note>佉<note place="inline">上聲</note>囉佉<note place="inline">上聲</note>囉<note place="inline">一</note>
<lb n="0928b12" ed="T"/>乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>野蘖賀禰<note place="inline">一</note>吽吽<note place="inline">一</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0928b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0928b1301">無盡意菩薩。復有普請阿彌陀如來阿閦如
<lb n="0928b14" ed="T"/>來毘盧遮那如來真言。及想三佛種智字亦
<lb n="0928b15" ed="T"/>應受持。若復有人建置壇場。請五阿闍梨。各
<lb n="0928b16" ed="T"/>想自身為釋迦牟尼佛寶閣。然請三佛及想
<lb n="0928b17" ed="T"/>種智。念此普請真言一七遍。</p>
